}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device is a '''Cameo''' WLG-2206 / '''Global Sun''' WL RT 2454 NM2.
Flash may be a 1MB '''Macronix''' MX29LV800BTC-90.
The board is marked with "WL RT 2454 NM2 B10 VER:V1-0" in the FCC photos.
